suncertify.db

Class SubcontractorRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • suncertify.db.SubcontractorRecord
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class SubcontractorRecord
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The SubcontractorRecord class represents a subcontractor record. It contains all fields that relate to a subcontractor record including the initial valid byte value. This class is used in both the data and business layers to represent a subcontractor record. It is serializable because it will need to travel from one VM to another when the application is running in server mode
    Author:
    Kieran O'Brien
